</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>【報價】POCO F4 GT 電競手機發佈　外形　功能　硬件　香港定價　發售詳情公佈</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/05/10/poco-f4-gt-hk-launch-price-revealed/mobile-phone/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=poco-f4-gt-hk-launch-price-revealed</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Edward]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Tue, 10 May 2022 05:05:30 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[手提電話]]></category><category><![CDATA[潮流手錶]]></category><category><![CDATA[音樂耳機]]></category><category><![CDATA[Buds Pro 原神特別版]]></category><category><![CDATA[F4 GT]]></category><category><![CDATA[Poco]]></category><category><![CDATA[POCO Watch]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1099053</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>早前 POCO 就宣佈推出中國 Redmi K50 電競版的國際版 F4 GT，作為今年第一部電競級旗艦手機， [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>早前 POCO 就宣佈推出中國 Redmi K50 電競版的國際版 F4 GT，作為今年第一部電競級旗艦手機，而此機今日就在香港正式推出。究竟有甚麼特別功能？香港發售詳情又如何？就讓 Edward 帶大家到現場睇一睇吧。</p><h2>效能強勁電競級別</h2><p>電競手機一向主打效能，POCO F4 GT 亦不例外，它內建了今年 Qualcomm 的旗艦級處理器 Snapdragon 8 Gen 1 及 Adreno 730 圖像處理晶片，配合 12GB LPDDR5 RAM 及 256GB UFS 3.1 內置儲存空間，效能上絕對是旗艦表現。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/20220510_114507.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1099073" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/20220510_114507-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/20220510_114507-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/20220510_114507-1280x721.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/20220510_114507-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/20220510_114507-1536x865.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/20220510_114507.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Screenshot_2022-04-25-18-16-45-838_com.finalwire.aida64.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1099058 alignnone" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Screenshot_2022-04-25-18-16-45-838_com.finalwire.aida64-261x580.jpg" alt="" width="261" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Screenshot_2022-04-25-18-16-45-838_com.finalwire.aida64-261x580.jpg 261w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Screenshot_2022-04-25-18-16-45-838_com.finalwire.aida64-405x900.jpg 405w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Screenshot_2022-04-25-18-16-45-838_com.finalwire.aida64-768x1707.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Screenshot_2022-04-25-18-16-45-838_com.finalwire.aida64-691x1536.jpg 691w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Screenshot_2022-04-25-18-16-45-838_com.finalwire.aida64.jpg 720w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 261px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Screenshot_2022-04-25-18-17-13-524_com.finalwire.aida64.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1099059 alignnone" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Screenshot_2022-04-25-18-17-13-524_com.finalwire.aida64-261x580.jpg" alt="" width="261" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Screenshot_2022-04-25-18-17-13-524_com.finalwire.aida64-261x580.jpg 261w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Screenshot_2022-04-25-18-17-13-524_com.finalwire.aida64-405x900.jpg 405w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Screenshot_2022-04-25-18-17-13-524_com.finalwire.aida64-768x1707.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Screenshot_2022-04-25-18-17-13-524_com.finalwire.aida64-691x1536.jpg 691w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Screenshot_2022-04-25-18-17-13-524_com.finalwire.aida64.jpg 720w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 261px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Screenshot_2022-04-25-18-16-50-024_com.finalwire.aida64.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1099057 alignnone" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Screenshot_2022-04-25-18-16-50-024_com.finalwire.aida64-261x580.jpg" alt="" width="261" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Screenshot_2022-04-25-18-16-50-024_com.finalwire.aida64-261x580.jpg 261w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Screenshot_2022-04-25-18-16-50-024_com.finalwire.aida64-405x900.jpg 405w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Screenshot_2022-04-25-18-16-50-024_com.finalwire.aida64-768x1707.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Screenshot_2022-04-25-18-16-50-024_com.finalwire.aida64-691x1536.jpg 691w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Screenshot_2022-04-25-18-16-50-024_com.finalwire.aida64.jpg 720w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 261px" /></a></p><h2>全新散熱系統面積夠大</h2><p>為了配合全新的硬件配置，POCO F4 GT 在散熱上亦有相關配合，它內建了全新一代的 LiquidCool 3.0 散熱技術，以合共 4,860mm2 的大面積雙導熱板，加上 6,904mm2 超大石墨烯層、3D 高功率石墨及其他物料，令手機高效運作時發出的熱量可以由內至外有效分層傳遞，令手機既可長時間高效運作，但熱力也不會困於機內導致影響表現，對於喜歡長時間打機的用家來說，看起來確實是十分體貼的設計。至於效果是否真如官方所言？採用全新散熱系統後手機又會否辣手？這就有待稍後借得真機後再為大家詳細實測了。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/DSC07957.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1099060" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/DSC07957-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/DSC07957-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/DSC07957-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/DSC07957-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/DSC07957-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/DSC07957.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2>針對愛打機用家而設</h2><p>POCO F4 GT 亦有不少設計及配置，是針對喜歡玩手機遊戲的用家而設。首先它內建彈出式遊戲鍵，令大家橫向打機時，機身可以多 2 個實體按鍵，而且更可以按不同遊戲需要而自行 map 按鍵的功能，對於打機的用家，尤其是愛玩 MMORPG、MOBA、動作類或運動競技類遊戲的用家，確實是十分不錯的設計。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/DSC07947.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1099061" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/DSC07947-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/DSC07947-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/DSC07947-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/DSC07947-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/DSC07947-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/DSC07947.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/DSC07948.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1099062" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/DSC07948-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/DSC07948-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/DSC07948-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/DSC07948-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/DSC07948-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/DSC07948.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/DSC07973.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1099063" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/DSC07973-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/DSC07973-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/DSC07973-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/DSC07973-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/DSC07973-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/DSC07973.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>另外，它附送 L 型 USB-C 充電線，令用家想邊玩邊充電時，充電線頭也不會頂著手掌，打機時自然更舒服。此外，它亦內建專用遊戲天線、Multi-Link 5.0 技術令系統可按網絡表現在 Wi-Fi 及 5G 連線之間自動切換等，也令大家玩線上遊戲時有更穩定的表現。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/DSC07937.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1099064" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/DSC07937-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/DSC07937-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/DSC07937-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/DSC07937-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/DSC07937-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/DSC07937.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>音效上，它內建四個以對稱設計的 JBL 喇叭單元，分別是一對雙高音喇叭及一對低音喇叭，更支援 Dolby Atmos 音效，令大家打機時可以享有不俗的音質效果；如果打機時要與隊友以語音溝通，它更內建 3 組咪高風，分別位於（橫向拿機時）機身左、右側及下方，無論用家如何拿著手機，都不用擔心咪高風位被遮蓋而影響語音表現。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/DSC07951.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1099065" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/DSC07951-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/DSC07951-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/DSC07951-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/DSC07951-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/DSC07951-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/DSC07951.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/DSC07953.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1099066" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/DSC07953-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/DSC07953-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/DSC07953-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/DSC07953-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/DSC07953-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/DSC07953.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>當然，對於電競用家來說，RGB 燈也是不可少的功能，而 POCO F4 GT 亦有類似設計，它的鏡頭模組中內建了 RGB 燈，不但會在 Game Turbo 模式開啟時亮起，有來電、訊息或電池開始充電時亦會閃起不同顏色的燈光，低調得來十分有型。此外，它的補光燈亦採用成閃電設計，整體設計上確實入型入格。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/DSC07961.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1099067" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/DSC07961-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/DSC07961-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/DSC07961-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/DSC07961-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/DSC07961-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/DSC07961.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2>120Hz 熒幕打機更暢順</h2><p>至於顯示方面，POCO F4 GT 內建了 6.67 吋 FHD+ AMOLED 熒幕，不過對於喜歡打機的用家，更重要的肯定是熒幕支援最高 120Hz 更新率，不但平常快速翻頁時有更暢順的效果，如果遊戲能支援高更新率的話，打機時也會有更流暢的表現。此外，熒幕更支援高達 480Hz 的觸控採樣率，換言之觸控熒幕到在遊戲中角色有反應的時間大大縮短，幾可說是近乎即時，兩者配合起來打機時自然可以制敵機先，玩 MOBA 或動作類的遊戲時絕對有一定幫助。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Screenshot_2022-04-25-19-48-04-625_com.xiaomi.misettings.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1099068" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Screenshot_2022-04-25-19-48-04-625_com.xiaomi.misettings-261x580.jpg" alt="" width="261" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Screenshot_2022-04-25-19-48-04-625_com.xiaomi.misettings-261x580.jpg 261w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Screenshot_2022-04-25-19-48-04-625_com.xiaomi.misettings-405x900.jpg 405w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Screenshot_2022-04-25-19-48-04-625_com.xiaomi.misettings-768x1707.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Screenshot_2022-04-25-19-48-04-625_com.xiaomi.misettings-691x1536.jpg 691w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Screenshot_2022-04-25-19-48-04-625_com.xiaomi.misettings.jpg 720w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 261px" /></a></p><h2>支援 120W 超快充回電極快</h2><p>至於電量方面，POCO F4 GT 內建了 4,700mAh 容量電池，不過重點是它支援 120W 超快充技術，而且隨機亦有附送 120W 超快充火牛，在手機閒置情況下，只需要 17 分鐘就可以由 0% 充滿至 100%；而即使打機時，也只需要 27 分鐘。這樣即使手機沒電，大家也不用擔心要暫停打機為手機充電那麼麻煩了。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/DSC07939.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1099069" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/DSC07939-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/DSC07939-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/DSC07939-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/DSC07939-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/DSC07939-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/DSC07939.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2>同場加映：POCO Buds Pro 原神特別版 + POCO Watch</h2><p>除了 POCO F4 GT 外，早前發佈會中發佈的 POCO Buds Pro 原神特別版及 POCO Watch，亦有在今日的香港發佈會中正式宣佈推出。先說 POCO Buds Pro 原神特別版吧，實際上它在功能及外型上完全與 Redmi Buds 3 Pro 一樣，只是外型加入了《原神》其中一個遊戲角色 Klee 的原素：充電盒及耳機採用桃紅色為主調的設計，就連耳機充電盒保護套也採用 Klee 揹包的設計樣式，而耳機的提示語也加入 Klee 的聲音，如果你是原神《Klee》的支持者，應該會十分喜歡這隻特別版真無線耳機。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/20220510_115302.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1099074" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/20220510_115302-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/20220510_115302-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/20220510_115302-1280x721.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/20220510_115302-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/20220510_115302-1536x865.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/20220510_115302.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>至於 POCO Watch，是 POCO 旗下首隻平價智能手錶，內建了 1.6 吋 AMOLED 熒幕，及包括心跳偵測器在內的多種感測器，不但可以量度心跳、血氧等，更可以作睡眠監測。另外，它支援 5ATM 防水功能，戴著游水都無問題；而且內建超過 100 種運動模式，更內建支援多種 GPS 系統，即使做運動時不帶手機跟身，也可以準確紀錄所經路徑在內的多種運動數據。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/20220510_115129.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1099075" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/20220510_115129-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/20220510_115129-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/20220510_115129-1280x721.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/20220510_115129-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/20220510_115129-1536x865.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/20220510_115129.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2>即日發佈定價發表</h2><p>至於推出詳情方面，3 款產品均會明日，即 5 月 11 日正式賣街。POCO F4 GT 設有隱士黑、黑爵銀及破曉黃 3 色選擇，香港只設有 12GB + 256GB 一種配置，定價為 $4,999，十分抵玩。至於 POCO Buds Pro 原神特別版真無線耳機及 POCO Watch 智能手錶，兩者定價均為 $549，同樣抵玩。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/20220510_114327.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1099076" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/20220510_114327-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/20220510_114327-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/20220510_114327-1280x721.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/20220510_114327-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/20220510_114327-1536x865.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/20220510_114327.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
